divs: Sighting DetailsY !! U will just tell the govt !! And we will not hear a thing from u !! That's to bad !! cause, the real warriors have a lot to show an say !! that's y we haven't tried before, cause we do not trust any of yr sites!! cause i think most of u r part of the problem !! and u just want Intel, on what we know!!! PLEASE !!! PROVE ME, WRONG !! PS. I was born an raised in salida co. Lived in Arizona, Washington DC, and have worked in Wyoming's oil and gas fields. WE have seen more than our share, and know first hand of lies and deception !!But still hoping that in my 47yrs,there is someone, who cares for mankind and the little guy !!! but we haven't found them yet!!
